T*
() Tj
T*
(This document describes how Atho uses SHA3-384 for identity, transaction hashing, and) Tj
T*
(addressing, and how Base56 encoding wraps hashed public keys \(HPK\). It also lists the code paths) Tj
T*
(involved and audit notes.) Tj
