T*
(- sha3\(data\): SHA3-384, returns 48-byte digest.) Tj
T*
(- sha3_hex\(data\): SHA3-384, returns 96-char lowercase hex.) Tj
T*
(- sha3_256 / sha3_256_hex: SHA3-256 helpers \(used for checksums\).) Tj
T*
(- Merkle helpers use SHA3-384 for parent/root computation.) Tj
