(HPK \(hashed public key\) generation and storage) Tj
T*
(- Public keys are Falcon-512 \(2048 hex chars\). HPK is sha3_384\(pubkey_bytes\).hex\(\) \(96 hex) Tj
T*
(chars\), typically prefixed with the internal network tag \(ATHO mainnet, ATHT testnet\).) Tj
T*
(- Key import/generation:) Tj
T*
(- Src/Accounts/key_manager.py: derives HPK when adding keys; enforce_cli_only\(\) ensures) Tj
T*
(CLI-format keys with HPK present; also uses sha3_384 in address export helpers.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Accounts/change_default_key.py: import helper routes materials through KeyManager) Tj
T*
(validation/HPK recompute before persistence.) Tj
T*
(- HPK is the canonical on-chain address binding \(hashed_public_key fields in outputs/UTXO\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Base56 address encoding \(Src/Blockchain/base56.py\)) Tj
T*
(- Alphabet: 23456789ABCDEFGHJKMNPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghjkmnpqrstuvwxyz \(56 chars, no visually) Tj
T*
(ambiguous symbols\).) Tj
T*
(- Input: HPK hex \(96 chars\), with or without internal prefix \(ATHO/ATHT\).) Tj
T*
(- Encoding:) Tj
T*
(- Convert HPK hex ? 48 bytes.) Tj
T*
(- Prefix: A \(mainnet\) or T \(testnet/regnet\).) Tj
T*
(- Body: prefix + base56\(raw_hpk_bytes\).) Tj
T*
(- Checksum: first 4 bytes of sha3_256\(body\) encoded base56, padded to 6 chars.) Tj
T*
(- Final address: <prefix><body><checksum>.) Tj
T*
(- Decoding:) Tj
T*
(- Verifies prefix matches expected network \(or Constants.NETWORK when enforced\).) Tj
T*
(- Recomputes checksum with sha3_256 and compares.) Tj
T*
(- Returns HPK hex \(padded to 96 chars\) and network; can re-add internal prefix.) Tj
T*
(- Normalization helper: normalize_hpk accepts either Base56 address or prefixed HPK and returns) Tj
T*
(the internal HPK string.) Tj
T*
(- Consumers:) Tj
T*
(- Wallet/CLI: Src/GUI/cliui.py and wallet APIs render Base56 for users, normalize back to HPK) Tj
T*
(internally.) Tj
T*
(- Tx construction: Src/Main/send.py resolves recipient/change via normalize_hpk.) Tj
T*
(- UTXO lookup: Src/Transactions/txmanager.py normalizes HPK for spend selection.) Tj
